http://www.sohu.com/a/427862013_362042	22251
<p> <span>央广网合肥</span><span>10</span><span>月</span><span>28</span><span>日消息（记者王利</span><span>通讯员李逸云）</span><span>10</span><span>月份是全国</span><span>“</span><span>敬老月</span><span>”</span><span>，安徽各地纷纷开展特色</span><span>“</span><span>敬老月</span><span>”</span><span>活动，共建共享老年友好社会，尊老爱老蔚然成风。</span></p>
